<script>
import $ from "jquery"
export default {
    data() {
        return {
            isActive: [],
            enableMenuBtn: false,
            enableMenuBar: false
        }
    },

    mounted() {
        if(window.innerWidth < 1100) {
            this.enableMenuBtn = true
            for (let index = 0; index < $(".header-cp .header-item").length; index++) {
                var element = $(".header-cp .header-item")[index]
                $(element).css("cssText", "display: none");
            }
        }else {
            this.enableMenuBtn = false
            for (let index = 0; index < $(".header-cp .header-item").length; index++) {
                element = $(".header-cp .header-item")[index]
                $(element).css("cssText", "display: block");
            }
        }
        window.addEventListener('resize', () => {
            if(window.innerWidth < 1100) {
                this.enableMenuBtn = true
                for (let index = 0; index < $(".header-cp .header-item").length; index++) {
                    var element = $(".header-cp .header-item")[index]
                    $(element).css("cssText", "display: none");
                }
            }else {
                this.enableMenuBtn = false
                for (let index = 0; index < $(".header-cp .header-item").length; index++) {
                    element = $(".header-cp .header-item")[index]
                    $(element).css("cssText", "display: block");
                }
            }
        })
        for (let index = 0; index < 4; index++) {
            this.isActive[index] = false}
        this.$set(this.isActive, 0, true)
    },

    methods: {
        showMenuBar() {
            this.enableMenuBar = !this.enableMenuBar
        },
        goToIntro() {
            for (let index = 0; index < 4; index++) {
                this.isActive[index] = false
            }
            this.$set(this.isActive, 0, true)

        },
        goToVR() {
            for (let index = 0; index < 4; index++) {

            }
            this.$set(this.isActive, 1, true)
            this.enableMenuBar = false
        },
        goToQA() {
            for (let index = 0; index < 4; index++) {
                this.isActive[index] = false
            }
            this.$set(this.isActive, 2, true)
            this.enableMenuBar = false
        },
        goToBrokerage() {
            for (let index = 0; index < 4; index++) {
                this.isActive[index] = false
            }
            this.$set(this.isActive, 3, true)
            this.enableMenuBar = false
        },
        openLoginDlg() {
            this.enableMenuBar = false
            $(".login-dlg").css("cssText", "display:block");
        }
    }
}
